ServerStatus: $serverStatus - Gives the current status of the MC server.
Version: $version - Gives the Git SHA of the current bot version running
CoinFlip: $coinflip - Flips a coin, sends gif for results
LMGTFY: {lmgtfy Reaction} - Add the 'Ask' Reaction to a msg and get a LMGTFY link
Play: $play {youtube_link} - Adds youtube audio to queue and plays it
